        <sponsor name-id="S352">Mr. Heller</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="S198">Mr. Reid</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S221">Mrs. Feinstein</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSEG00">Committee on Energy and Natural Resources</committee-name>
